entries.femaleVariant: Impressive pharmacy... Didn't even know this stuff was still on the black market.
Pretty girls... Look a lot alike.
Sisters?
A safe behind a painting... A little cliché, but hey, at least the merc 'preciates the arts. You could learn a thing or two.
Yeah... Somethin' twisted happened here, V.
If life's taught me one thing, it's that a safe's a good spot to hide your valuables.
Got a reader, too. Must be an access shard around...
entries.maleVariant: It's got a reader, too. Must be an access shard around...

entries.femaleVariant: All these pills are downers. They're what you get if you can afford better. Helluva lot for one person here.
Wonderin' more how it ended up on the ground. Juliet must've been in a hurry.
Could be. Man, this still is ancient. And if Juliet's one of 'em, question is who's the other.
I'm startin' to like this less and less. Best stay on our toes.
Someone took a nasty hit on this.
To put it mildly.
Almost completely used up...
Not something you'd keep in your medicine cabinet.
What a mess – reeks, too... Usual hallmarks of a merc's room stop there...
Signs of a struggle?
First-aid kit...
Fuck...
Look what we have here...
Interesting...
It's locked.
